A vintage-style illustration of a late afternoon picnic scene at a tropical seaside park, featuring a woven basket with golden pan-fried chicken pieces on a checkered blanket, surrounded by fresh baguettes, scattered cranberries, and sprigs of parsley. In the background, palm trees sway gently against a warm amber sky, with calm waters stretching to a distant coastline visible on the horizon. A small speedboat creates a white wake in the water. The scene is bathed in soft golden hour light with muted, warm tones reminiscent of 1960s travel postcards, with slightly faded colors and a subtle grain texture throughout.
